# Input

```scss
$a:10;
$b:20;

$expr-1:10 +#{$a};
$expr-2:#{$a}* #{$b};
$expr-3:10*#{10};
$expr-4:#{$a}/#{$b}/#{$c};
$expr-5:-#{$a}/#{$b};

foo{
  plus:10+#{10};
  minus:10 - #{10};
  slash:10/#{10};
  eq:10==#{10};
  ne:10!=#{10};
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
$a: 10;
$b: 20;

$expr-1: 10 +#{$a};
$expr-2: #{$a}* #{$b};
$expr-3: 10 *#{10};
$expr-4: #{$a}/#{$b}/#{$c};
$expr-5: -#{$a}/#{$b};

foo {
	plus: 10 +#{10};
	minus: 10 - #{10};
	slash: 10 /#{10};
	eq: 10==#{10};
	ne: 10!=#{10};
}

```
